N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 2507.2 - Proceedings instituted by the division

State Regulations

The division may institute, reclassify, or convert a
proceeding on its own initiative whenever the division deems it necessary or
appropriate pursuant to the act or this Chapter. Notes
